## 4. The V3 diagnostic mapping table (descriptive)

Per the Phase 2h spec, V3-side candidates examined are: `K_G`, `condition_number`, `near_umbilic_label`, `lifted_singularity_null_direction`, `hessian_eigenvalue_diagnostics`.

Allowed per-pair relations: `direct_analogue`, `diagnostic_neighbour`, `oracle_crosscheck_only`, `not_supported`, `not_applicable_in_1d`.

